latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I love to sing🎤. I may not sound good or I may dazzle you with my skills, but I still love to sing. I wanted to improve, learn, grow, and luckily I found just the person who could help me .....my lil sister.
.
She taught me the peculiarities of singing a song properly,like Taal and Sur ...and also too never go off scale😂😂....
.
I can't thank her enough for guiding me through this song..❤️
